%%{init: {"theme": "neutral"}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> needs_run : gate registered

    needs_run --> clean : run_command passes
    needs_run --> dirty : run_command fails

    clean --> stale : expires or watch_paths changed
    clean --> dirty : run_command fails

    stale --> clean : re-run passes
    stale --> dirty : re-run fails

    dirty --> clean : fix + re-run passes
